================================================================================
IMPORTANT NOTICE REGARDING ROM FILES
====================================

This software is a hardware emulation / hardware recreation system. It does
not include proprietary ROM files, firmware images, monitor ROMs, BASIC ROMs,
KERNAL ROMs, character ROMs or other original system software from historical
computers.

The ROM files for the following systems may be required but are NOT PROVIDED:

* Commodore 64: BASIC, KERNAL, CHARGEN
* VIC-20: BASIC, KERNAL, CHARGEN
* Commodore 16: BASIC, KERNAL
* ZX Spectrum: 48K ROM
* Apple I / Apple II: monitor, BASIC, character generator or related ROMs
* Atari 800: OS, BASIC

Users must obtain any required ROM or firmware files legally from:

1. original hardware they own;
2. licensed distributors;
3. official sources where available;
4. other lawful sources.

The authors of this software do not condone, encourage or support piracy.

